    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the scientist manage the routine tasks of an indoor farm in a cold, lonely world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together, you can keep the farm running and maybe do a little bit of good for humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;What more is there to do? We feed millions of people across the world. And if this place is still standing in a few months, it might just end up feeding the entire world.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;I guess.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;You guess?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;It’s just like...why did we build all this, if we’re just going to use it to survive another day?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short and atmospheric linear visual novel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemplation in a post-apocalyptic setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bold and expressive pixel art</p></li></ul>",
